response.overview: A farm girl is on an epic quest to recover a cherished family heirloom. Her journey leads her to a strange and dangerous city where she meets her one true love – but in order to save his soul, she must put the power of destiny and song to the ultimate test.
response.tagline: Ain’t nothing more powerful than love.
response.title: O'Dessa

release_dates.note: South by Southwest Film & TV Festival
